  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served each morning in the dining room and offers freshly baked pastries, breads, cold cuts, yogurts and fruit. All complimented by freshly brewed coffees and teas. </p>
<p>Dinner is four courses with a choice of dishes ranging from traditional Italian cuisine such as spaghetti vongole to European fusion dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
